<% layout('layouts/infoBoilerplate') -%>

    <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-gray-900 to-gray-800 pt-20 pb-16 relative overflow-hidden">
        <div
            class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-full opacity-10 bg-[url('https://www.transparenttextures.com/patterns/cubes.png')]">
        </div>
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10 text-center" data-aos="fade-up">
            <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-white mb-4 tracking-tight">
                <i class="fas fa-clipboard-list text-[#fe424d] mr-3"></i> Host Guidelines
            </h1>
            <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Maintain high standards and ensure exceptional guest
                experiences with our community guidelines.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 py-16">
        <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-12">

            <div class="lg:w-1/4 hidden lg:block">
                <div
                    class="sticky top-28 bg-white border border-gray-100 rounded-3xl p-6 shadow-[0_8px_30px_rgb(0,0,0,0.04)]">
                    <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 uppercase tracking-wider text-sm flex items-center gap-2">
                        <i class="fas fa-list text-[#fe424d]"></i> Contents
                    </h3>
                    <nav class="sticky-nav flex flex-col space-y-1">
                        <a href="#accuracy"
                            class="px-4 py-2 text-sm text-gray-500 rounded-lg border-l-2 border-transparent hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors">Listing
                            Accuracy</a>
                        <a href="#cleanliness"
                            class="px-4 py-2 text-sm text-gray-500 rounded-lg border-l-2 border-transparent hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors">Cleanliness
                            Standards</a>
                        <a href="#communication"
                            class="px-4 py-2 text-sm text-gray-500 rounded-lg border-l-2 border-transparent hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors">Communication</a>
                        <a href="#safety"
                            class="px-4 py-2 text-sm text-gray-500 rounded-lg border-l-2 border-transparent hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors">Safety
                            Requirements</a>
                    </nav>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div
                class="lg:w-3/4 prose-content bg-white p-8 md:p-12 rounded-3xl shadow-[0_8px_30px_rgb(0,0,0,0.04)] border border-gray-100">

                <div id="accuracy">
                    <h2><i class="fas fa-bullseye"></i> Listing Accuracy</h2>
                    <p>Trust begins with a truthful listing. Guests should know exactly what to expect before they
                        arrive.</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Use recent, unedited photos that accurately depict the current state of your property.</li>
                        <li>Clearly list all available amenities and note if any are currently out of order.</li>
                        <li>Be honest about potential drawbacks, such as street noise or steep stairs.</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div id="cleanliness">
                    <h2><i class="fas fa-broom"></i> Cleanliness Standards</h2>
                    <p>Cleanliness is one of the most important factors in receiving a 5-star review.</p>
                    <div class="highlight-box">
                        <h4><i class="fas fa-sparkles"></i> The 5-Step Enhanced Cleaning Process</h4>
                        <p>All hosts are required to follow our enhanced cleaning protocol: Prepare, Clean, Sanitize,
                            Check, and Reset.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div id="communication">
                    <h2><i class="fas fa-comments"></i> Communication Guidelines</h2>
                    <p>Be responsive, polite, and helpful before, during, and after a guest's stay.</p>
                    <ol>
                        <li>Aim to respond to all inquiries and booking requests within 24 hours.</li>
                        <li>Provide clear check-in instructions at least 48 hours before arrival.</li>
                        <li>Be available (or provide a reliable co-host's contact info) to assist guests in case of an
                            emergency.</li>
                    </ol>
                </div>

                <div id="safety">
                    <h2><i class="fas fa-hard-hat"></i> Safety Requirements</h2>
                    <p>Your property must meet basic safety requirements to be listed on Stayzio.</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Install working smoke and carbon monoxide detectors in appropriate areas.</li>
                        <li>Provide a clearly marked and easily accessible first-aid kit.</li>
                        <li>Display a list of emergency local numbers (police, hospital, fire department) inside the
                            property.</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

            </div>
        </div>
    </div>